                "imgDesc": "<p>The odd gems called Scarlet Quartzes contain a certain kind of warming energy. <span style=\"color: #FFE14B\">Break them and collect their fragments</span> to engulf your character in that energy.</p>",
                "key": "Page 1/2"
              },
