                "imgDesc": "<p>Under its influence, <span style=\"color: #FFE14B\">you will stop accumulating Sheer Cold</span>. You can use this effect to keep warm for an extended period. Attack and opponent before its duration ends to release all the accumulated energy at once.<br>For some reason, however, warping from here to a Teleport Waypoint or a Statue of The Seven will cause <span style=\"color: #FFE14B\">the power of these</span> <span style=\"color: #FFE14B\">Scarlet Quartzes to dissipate</span>...</p>",
